      },
      "writtenOn": "2017-01-30T15:42:30Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So Mike and I talked about this briefly last week. If we return a bool here than we need a check inside the DRAW_LOOPER macro on SkCanvas. Yet really if the first one succeeds in that loop than all the others should as well. So I believe the idea was it becomes easier to read/understand the flow in SkCanvas with this approach. Though either is equally valid, so happy to do whatever.",
      "revId": "c2df20022382b2f083b28e82cd0ef0de27bbc8c9",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
      "unresolved": true
    },
